OOC: Well this Prowl has been in the Neo Beast Wars, and has held a high
position with these Maximals longer. Plus Hot Rod doesn't like the
burden of command.

::Hot Rod::

He can see the stranded bots become larger as he closes in. Suddenly his
form leaps up transforming to bot mode, and landing in front of them.
"Hello. I'm Hot Rod from the Maximals. The commander will be here
shortly."

OOC: Your chars may notice the Autobot logo on Hot Rod, since your
expecting Maximals from that faction. Even though he serves with the
Maximals, he is an Autobot.
